ote><br />\n屌，連登呢啲垃圾論壇唔上都把撚就啦。唔好為左呢啲小問題而影響用nokia嘅信心，ok ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你又上</blockquote><br />\n為左眾生皆用nokia, 我不入地獄誰入地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁巴打你用緊邊部nokia機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d22382dc2e04e769984c737913c27a17aad08d","tid":326594,"uid":12628,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:19:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Iphone呢啲垃圾，唔掉唔撚得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔得喎，android個lihkg app太垃圾，打死都唔轉機</blockquote><br />\n屌，連登呢啲垃圾論壇唔上都把撚就啦。唔好為左呢啲小問題而影響用nokia嘅信心，ok ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你又上</blockquote><br />\n為左眾生皆用nokia, 我不入地獄誰入地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁巴打你用緊邊部nokia機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好問題，介紹返你我嘅愛機：<br />\n當Samsung Note 7又爆炸，S8又價錢高效能低，iPhone 7更是業界垃圾; 此情況下，<span style=\"color: red;\">「防爆之王」、「地表最強」的Nokia最強手機Nokia216。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/161919_493bf9908f7891aeb6b366b751fb48f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F161919_493bf9908f7891aeb6b366b751fb48f9.jpg&h=0cd035f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/161919_c56d56adf639e41adba5c168a7849723.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F161919_c56d56adf639e41adba5c168a7849723.jpg&h=808dada1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNokia 216售價只是388元，配置雙卡雙待版除支援上網功能，亦配備前後相機鏡頭和LED閃光燈，提升攝影質素。此外，它內置FM收音機、MP3及視頻播放器，更可以藍牙耳機提供音頻傳輸，並可儲存高達2,000項聯絡人資料，並支援高達32GB的記憶卡。<br />\n該手機有黑色及藍色，機身外殼採用聚碳酸酯材料製作，<br />\n實為「外觀型格優美、堅固耐用」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d99ca79cecfd558b220d2939adaa74ee912f8d7","tid":326594,"uid":66351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:21:29.000Z","msg":"in木馬 we trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad6d6d9c7c1ec7ab4c7f00c33c5584c3af934155","tid":326594,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:53:20.000Z","msg":"之後 賠返部3310俾人當無數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9513ee74d46bcec81859aebfae57231a81086641","tid":326594,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T10:09:20.000Z","msg":"Nokia 216, 真正生活上最好嘅拍檔"},{"pid":"419f60220c95a9fc7f8325809c1b398ab8f12b52","tid":326594,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T10:14:42.000Z","msg":"老人家專用"},{"pid":"787d0767ca76f748c29a0ff25e86dea932ccfdb6","tid":326594,"uid":78165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T10:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef53cc5d969853bd38c5701d0a12024493575391","tid":326594,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T10:24:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老人家專用</blockquote><br />\n依家啲機好新潮，功能強勁為業界之尖端，唔是老人機呀ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/182443_8cd6d5d45a69530e6e0bdc06052e2f46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F182443_8cd6d5d45a69530e6e0bdc06052e2f46.jpg&h=f2ac55d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"