。</span><br />\n呢啲就係先見之明！皇者睇事情就係高人一級目光遠大！<br />\n依家nokia出android phone唔係最終結果，呢個只係開始，最後嘅勝利者，將係未來嘅nokia !"},{"pid":"e4d7d0ecea439ee4f77360156e8dccf209b38f8b","tid":326594,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T02:14:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce77eccb0dbd0163d829302d4f82a809e5b5d3e7","tid":326594,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T04:42:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33f138bc919fab282e821d743da9f0ef4742614","tid":326594,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T05:26:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfdc3ad30299528b4b5d805c2a2fa5dca02847b8","tid":326594,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T11:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6946b39786f594b1e7df51b8a77b32d12fd1df84","tid":326594,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:49:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"741aea3371e7f5524485bf6e20d3a18b3a1ac343","tid":326594,"uid":9284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:52:19.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"44903b017cddddf180d193aae51196a7dc3c5c66","tid":326594,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:08:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d47fbcb1cc9cb7577b8a7dfd07a647fe2550fe11","tid":326594,"uid":40547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T00:57:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://chinese.engadget.com/2017/07/19/hmd-global-replaces-its-ceo/?ncid=txtlnkusaolp00000595\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2Fhmd-global-replaces-its-ceo%2F%3Fncid%3Dtxtlnkusaolp00000595&d=wxg8iiEDpLG4QBOT5BMfm8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=1f23a777\" target=\"_blank\">http://chinese.engadget.com/2017/07/19/hmd-global-replaces-its-ceo/?ncid=txtlnkusaolp00000595</a><br />\n<br />\n沒想到在傳說中的 Nokia 8 真正到來以前，HMD Global 那邊卻突然傳來了 CEO 換人的意外消息。就在剛才，他們正式對外宣佈 CEO、董事會成員 Arto Nummela 在與公司協商後已經同意立即離開 HMD。2013 年離開 HTC 加盟 Nokia，後來與 Nummela 一同領導 HMD 的現任總裁 Florian Seiche，在保持原職務的同時，接下來也會代理 CEO 一職。<br />\n<br />\n老實講，這次人事變動突如其來，發生的時機還正巧在旗艦機流言的爆發期。而且 Arto Nummela 幾乎可看作是 Nokia 此番品牌回歸的第一「門面」，官方就這麼毫無徵兆地換帥，難免會讓人好奇背後究竟發生了什麼樣的事情啊。<br />\n<br />\n因為太串所以比炒?"},{"pid":"341a7a8392d15f67075ce6324c4560884fa11607","tid":326594,"uid":40547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T00:59:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://chinese.engadget.com/2017/07/19/hmd-global-replaces-its-ceo/?ncid=txtlnkusaolp00000595\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2Fhmd-global-replaces-its-ceo%2F%3Fncid%3Dtxtlnkusaolp00000595&d=wxg8iiEDpLG4QBOT5BMfm8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=1f23a777\" target=\"_blank\">http://chinese.engadget.com/2017/07/19/hmd-global-replaces-its-ceo/?ncid=txtlnkusaolp00000595</a><br />\n<br />\n沒想到在傳說中的 Nokia 8 真正到來以前，HMD Global 那邊卻突然傳來了 CEO 換人的意外消息。就在剛才，他們正式對外宣佈 CEO、董事會成員 Arto Nummela 在與公司協商後已經同意立即離開 HMD。2013 年離開 HTC 加盟 Nokia，後來與 Nummela 一同領導 HMD 的現任總裁 Florian Seiche，在保持原職務的同時，接下來也會代理 CEO 一職。<br />\n<br />\n老實講，這次人事變動突如其來，發生的時機還正巧在旗艦機流言的爆發期。而且 Arto Nummela 幾乎可看作是 Nokia 此番品牌回歸的第一「門面」，官方就這麼毫無徵兆地換帥，難免會讓人好奇背後究竟發生了什麼樣的事情啊。<br />\n<br />\n因為太串所以比炒?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSorry. 睇錯<br />\n係另一個 CEO ?"},{"pid":"bd33c96d2eb2be1bc65d9e2c871b25e92710dd1c","tid":326594,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T01:52:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinese.engadget.com/2017/07/19/hmd-global-replaces-its-ceo/?ncid=txtlnkusaolp00000595\" data-sr-url=